  "texts": [
    "Google has published results for ELIXR, a model capable of interpreting CXRs, but this model is not publicly available [8].",
    "Similarly, the open-source LLaVA-MED, a model tuned to the medical domain, has been released.",
    "However, detailed insights into its proficiency in interpreting CXRs remain limited [9].Radiologists' workload has significantly increased over the past three decades, potentially impacting the accuracy of radiologic diagnoses [10].",
    "In response, numerous studies have explored the use of deep learning models to improve diagnostic accuracy and reduce the burden on radiologists [11].",
    "Building on this line of research, our study employed the latest technology, a multimodal LLM, to attempt radiologic report generation for CXRs."
  ],
